Note on components and data (for downstream users):
- The Mambo code in this repository is MIT-licensed (above).
- It depends on permissively-licensed libraries (librosa, faster-whisper, numpy,
  pretty_midi, etc.); see each project for its terms.
- The OPTIONAL training track (finetune/) references third-party datasets/weights
  with their own, more restrictive terms (e.g. HumTrans CC BY-NC, Qwen2-Audio,
  MusicGen weights CC-BY-NC). Those are NOT part of the shipped modular pipeline
  and are not redistributed here; honor their licenses if you use that track.
- Human voice recordings of study volunteers are NOT included (git-ignored); only
  their derived metrics are committed. See the ethics statement in PAPER.md §7.1.
